snippet.title: Atari 5200 - Countermeasure © 1982 Atari - Gameplay
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
CONDITION RED! Terrorists have seized a silo complex and aimed the missiles at Washington, D.C. Blast the silos and save the country before the launch sequence timer runs out. Fail and your only hope is to guess the fail-safe code that disarms the missiles in the seconds before impact.
